reference-wr.title: Customer Logs Reference Table
reference-wr.shortdesc: The Customer Logs include events that do not require immediate user action.

section.p: The following types of events are included in the Customer Logs. The severity of the events is represented in the table by one or more letters, as follows:

stentry.p: Live-Migrate aborted for instance <instance-name>, reason=<reason for abort>
Guest Heartbeat failed for instance <instance-name>, soft-reboot repair action requested
Guest Heartbeat failed for instance <instance-name>, stop repair action requested
